00:51:32.405 --> 00:51:36.676 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We conclude this month’s program
by traveling to Indonesia.

00:51:36.676 --> 00:51:39.813 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Composed of more than 17,000 islands,

00:51:39.813 --> 00:51:42.783 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
it consists of hundreds of distinct native,

00:51:42.783 --> 00:51:45.152 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
ethnic, and linguistic groups,

00:51:45.152 --> 00:51:47.721 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with the largest being the Javanese.

00:51:47.721 --> 00:51:49.723 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s visit the city of Malang,

00:51:49.723 --> 00:51:52.626 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
which has some 370 publishers

00:51:52.626 --> 00:51:54.628 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in 9 congregations.

00:51:54.628 --> 00:51:56.797 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The territory here is productive,

00:51:56.797 --> 00:52:00.133 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with many who are open to the Bible’s message.

00:52:00.133 --> 00:52:04.771 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The largest challenge
our brothers face here is economic hardship.

00:52:04.771 --> 00:52:08.141 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s not easy to provide even basic necessities,

00:52:08.141 --> 00:52:12.078 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so many people in the territory work long hours.

00:52:12.078 --> 00:52:14.114 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
However, the pioneers

00:52:14.114 --> 00:52:16.783 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
have found an ingenious way to make a living

00:52:16.783 --> 00:52:19.920 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
making milk, juice, and cakes from soybeans.

00:52:19.920 --> 00:52:23.190 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
A typical day will have them up at 3:00 a.m.

00:52:23.190 --> 00:52:25.192 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
making fresh soy products

00:52:25.192 --> 00:52:29.029 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and then selling them
on the street in the morning.

00:52:29.029 --> 00:52:32.232 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the afternoon they preach
and go to the market that evening

00:52:32.232 --> 00:52:35.468 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to buy fresh ingredients
for the next day’s work.

00:52:36.603 --> 00:52:39.773 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
While the brothers in Malang
have not yet been able to obtain a permit

00:52:39.773 --> 00:52:43.743 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for an official Kingdom Hall,
they often meet in private homes.

00:52:43.743 --> 00:52:45.846 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Although it can be cramped and hot,

00:52:45.846 --> 00:52:49.616 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
attendance is
nearly always well over 100 percent.

00:52:49.616 --> 00:52:51.585 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The publishers in Malang

00:52:51.585 --> 00:52:54.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
send their warm love and greetings

00:52:54.020 --> 00:52:56.423 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to our entire global brotherhood.

00:52:57.490 --> 00:52:59.492 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is JW Broadcasting

00:52:59.492 --> 00:53:03.730 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from the world headquarters
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

